INSERT INTO supplierUsers (userId, supplierId, role, createdAt)
SELECT u.id, s.id, 'supplier_admin', NOW()
FROM users u, suppliers s 
WHERE u.email = 'apvirldtxuxegywado@nesopf.com' 
AND s.contactEmail = 'apvirldtxuxegywado@nesopf.com'
LIMIT 1;
